description: Cold-blooded hitman Louis Trent benefited from a life of dealing in death; the swank crib, the fine cars and slammin' honeys were his. Then like a fool he saved a kid and got killed for his effort. His trip to Hell interrupted, he's sent back to Earth to take out demons and devils, while he desperately tries to cancel his forced contract with Heaven.
name: The Devil's Handmaiden

description: In the War between Heaven & Hell, one soldier has been on the front lines of the battleground since the very Beginning. But now the ultimate angel of destruction has grown weary of her never-ending tour of duty & the world it’s waged on. After millennia of killing, Gabriel has begun to realize that even an eternal warrior needs more out of life than dealing death.
name: Raining Fire

volume.name: Marvel Knights: Ghost Rider, Autopista Al Infierno

description: She can’t control her urges. She extracts pieces of men’s souls while they sleep. She tried to switch sides during the fall, but that only resulted in her punishment…her banishment. She just wants to go home…to heaven…but no one seems to remember who she is.
name: Demon Lover

description: In the war between Heaven and Hell, all that stands between humanity and Arm[a]geddon are the shock troops Knights Templar. If that means preemptive strikes with some collateral damage, then so be it. Sleeping with the enemy? No problem. Betrayal may be just around the corner, but there will be no Apocalypse on their watch.
name: Honeypot

description: Heaven’s first rebel. Our world’s first curse. Trapped for a millennia within the skin of humanity, that fallen angel, WOLF, has vowed vengeance on the god who created his perfect cage.Now, after long last, he can taste the blood of revenge, and it is sweet.
name: Under My Skin
